name 'ai-powered-threats-defenses-postassessment-q5_2025-pilot'

question ‘How has the introduction of advanced AI tools, such as voice cloning, most significantly changed traditional phishing scams?’

wrong ‘It has shifted the primary goal of phishing from stealing data to spreading misinformation’
wrong ‘It has made all phishing attacks fully automated, requiring no human involvement’
right ‘It allows attackers to create highly personalized and believable scenarios that are harder to distinguish from reality’
wrong ‘It has made phishing attacks far more expensive and difficult to conduct’

allow_multiple_attempts true

